HEADWORD: Indignify
<hw>In*dig"ni*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>indignus</ets> unworthy + <ets>-fy</ets>.]</ety> <def>To treat
